description: Let F(x) = 1 + x + 4x^2 + 9x^3 + ... = g.f. for A002835 (solid partitions restricted to two planes) and expand (1-x)(1-x^2)(1-x^3)...*F(x) in powers of x.
references: D. E. Knuth, A note on solid partitions, Math. Comp., 24 (1970), 955-961.
N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
